# Project 4: Number Guessing Game with GUI

## Description
An interactive number guessing game with a graphical user interface (GUI) built using Tkinter. Players guess a random number between 1-100 with up to 10 attempts, receiving feedback (Too High/Too Low) after each guess.

## Skills Learned
- ✅ Tkinter GUI development
- ✅ Object-oriented programming (OOP)
- ✅ Event handling (button clicks, key presses)
- ✅ Random number generation
- ✅ Game logic and state management
- ✅ GUI layout (frames, widgets, packing)
- ✅ Message boxes and user feedback

## How to Run
```bash
python number_guessing_game.py
```

**Note:** Tkinter comes built-in with Python. No additional installation needed!

## Features
✅ Beautiful GUI interface with colors
✅ Random number generation (1-100)
✅ Real-time feedback (Too High/Too Low)
✅ Attempt counter (max 10 attempts)
✅ Guess history tracking
